### ==========================================
### Adeem API - IntelliJ HTTP Client Requests
### ==========================================
### كيف تستخدمه:
### 1. حط هذا الملف بأي مكان داخل مشروع IntelliJ (مثلاً مجلد اسمه http/)
### 2. شغل السيرفر (Spring Boot) أول
### 3. اضغط السهم الأخضر ▶️ جنب أي طلب تبيه
### 4. بعد الـ Login، انسخ التوكن من الرد والصقه بمكان {{token}} و {{doctorToken}} تحت يدوياً
###    (أو استخدم ملف http-client.env.json للمتغيرات التلقائية - شرحته في الرسالة)
### ==========================================


### ==================== AUTH & REGISTRATION ====================

### 1. Register Patient
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "patient@test.com",
  "password": "12345678",
  "fullName": "Patient Test",
  "phoneNumber": "0512345678"
}
### 2. Register Doctor
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/doctors/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "doctor@test.com",
  "password": "12345678",
  "fullName": "Doctor Test",
  "phoneNumber": "0512345679",
  "specialty": "Dermatology",
  "pricePerSession": 150,
  "licenseNumber": "LIC12345",
  "bio": "Experienced dermatologist"
}

### 3. Login as Patient (انسخ التوكن من الرد وحطه بمتغير token تحت)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "patient@test.com",
  "password": "12345678"
}

### 4. Login as Doctor (انسخ التوكن من الرد وحطه بمتغير doctorToken تحت)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "doctor@test.com",
  "password": "12345678"
}


### ==================== VARIABLES (عدلها يدوياً بعد كل login) ====================
### @token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9...  <- توكن المريض هنا
### @doctorToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9...  <- توكن الطبيب هنا


### ==================== USERS ====================

### 5. Get My Profile (Patient)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Update My Profile (Patient)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fullName": "Patient Updated Name",
  "phoneNumber": "0599999999"
}


### ==================== DOCTORS ====================

### 7. Get Verified Doctors (Public - no token needed)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/doctors/verified

### 8. Get My Doctor Profile
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/doctors/me
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}

### 9. Get Pending Doctors (Admin only - will fail unless you have an admin token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/doctors/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 10. Approve/Reject Doctor (Admin only)
### غيّر الـ {id} برقم الـ doctorProfile الفعلي
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/doctors/1/verification
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "VERIFIED"
}


### ==================== DOCTOR AVAILABILITY ====================

### 11. Doctor Adds Availability
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/availability
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dayOfWeek": "SUNDAY",
  "startTime": "09:00:00",
  "endTime": "17:00:00"
}

### 12. Get My Availability (Doctor)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/availability/me
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}

### 13. Get a Specific Doctor's Availability (Public)
### غيّر doctorId برقم بروفايل الطبيب الفعلي
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/availability/doctor/1


### ==================== APPOINTMENTS ====================

### 14. Get Available Slots for a Doctor on a Date (Public)
### تأكد التاريخ يوم "SUNDAY" فعلي (أو أي يوم ضفت له Availability)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments/available-slots?doctorId=1&date=2026-07-26

### 15. Book Appointment (Patient)
### تأكد appointmentDate يطابق أحد الـ slots اللي رجعت من الطلب اللي فوق
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doctorId": 1,
  "appointmentDate": "2026-07-26T09:00:00",
  "consultationType": "CHAT"
}

### 16. Get My Appointments (Patient)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments/my-appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 17. Get My Appointments (Doctor)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments/doctor-appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}

### 18. Cancel Appointment
### غيّر {id} برقم الموعد الفعلي
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ==================== NEGATIVE TESTS (يفترض ترجع خطأ) ====================

### 19. Access protected endpoint WITHOUT token -> يفترض 401
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me

### 20. Patient tries to access Admin-only endpoint -> يفترض 403
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/doctors/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Initiate Payment
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentId": 1
}

### Confirm Payment (انسخ transactionReference من الرد اللي فوق)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionReference": "MOCK-6CCF14B5-525"
}

### تأكد الموعد صار CONFIRMED
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/appointments/my-appointments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Send Message
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "appointmentId": 1,
  "content": "مرحباً دكتور، عندي استفسار"
}

### Get Conversation
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/messages/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

####
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/chatbot/ask
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "عندي طفح جلدي أحمر بالذراع من يومين"
}